  services: 'Our customs attorneys provide strategic counsel on prior disclosure timing, helping California importers assess filing windows, prepare protective disclosures, calculate interest versus penalty exposure, and coordinate multi-port submissions through California\'s major ports. We guide clients through tender requirements, perfection procedures, and the critical determination of whether CBP has commenced a formal investigation.',
