  services: 'Our CAFTA-DR textile compliance services include yarn-forward rule analysis, TPL quota management, origin determination under 19 CFR 10.2024, preferential treatment claims, verification response coordination, and Central American supply chain structuring. We assist California apparel companies with regulatory compliance audits, documentation preparation, and strategic sourcing optimization.',
